    <item>
      <title>美国经济：核心个人消费支出降温至 5 月以来最低水平</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-12-20/us-economy-core-pce-cools-to-slowest-pace-since-may-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美联储首选的衡量基础通胀的指标出现了自 5 月份以来最慢的月度涨幅。根据美国经济分析局周五公布的数据，所谓的核心个人消费支出价格指数（不包括食品和能源项目）较 10 月份上涨 0.1%，较上年同期上涨 2.8%。Michael McKee 提供了详细信息。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-12-20/us-economy-core-pce-cools-to-slowest-pace-since-may-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 20 Dec 2024 14:31:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美联储关键通胀数据落后于预期，美国国债上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-20/treasuries-gain-as-key-fed-inflation-figures-trails-estimates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于备受关注的通胀数据低于预期，美国国债价格上涨，导致交易员上调美联储明年降息预期。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-20/treasuries-gain-as-key-fed-inflation-figures-trails-estimates</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 20 Dec 2024 14:12:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
